Class MASFileObject

  • java.lang.Object

        Constructs MASFileObject using file bytes.
        Parameters:
        fileName - The file name.
        fileType - The mime type, eg. if file is sample.png the fileType should be "image/png".
        fieldName - The field name for the file, in case of file upload using http post.
        fileBytes - The file content as bytes.
